{"tid":251550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"買罐頭圖製政府HK20創意圖像    設計師蔡楚堅：似街坊會做法","createTime":"2017-05-21T04:52:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-22T13:00:53.000Z","uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d0e30aa2020f6a8a0e4e8855d680e791bac96962","tid":251550,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T04:52:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170519/large/1495190685_a286.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170519%2Flarge%2F1495190685_a286.jpg&h=c5fa01bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n20周年創意圖像周街都係，設計老土不在話下，潑彩色底竟然係圖像網素材，認真小學雞。<br />\n<br />\n大家最近出街，不論時運高低都會看到慶回歸20周年宣傳品，電燈柱上、摩天輪下、碼頭蓋頂、巴士車身，撞口撞面，避都避唔到。美術設計繁雜老土，屢受批評。連設計大師Henry Steiner都狠批：「根本達不到國際標準。」早前立法會議員鄭松泰facebook專頁質疑，其中一款慶回歸「創意圖像」一撻撻底色來自素材網站，新聞處直認不諱。<br />\n<br />\n鄭松泰議員斥政府「堆砌當原創」，絕非誇張。「慶祝活動」如斯大型，宣傳品卻用現成設計素材，毫不專業，真係好想瘋狂播100次Henry Steiner批評官方設計「垃圾」嗰句畀決策嗰位聽。政府新聞處書面回覆我們查詢，指該HK20潑彩創意圖像由他們設計組同事「設計」，承認色底從圖像網站購得，不過就補充一句是「經過處理」才應用。問到整個慶祝活動於設計方面花費多少公帑，就沒回答。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">「㷫回歸」多過「慶回歸」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n就此事我們訪問曾獲國際多個設計獎項的本地著名設計師蔡楚堅（Sandy），他說：「比較懶的設計師可能會這樣做，我冇興趣深究。嗰堆圖像設計點差，已經好多人評論過。我會形容做法好街坊會，好喜慶好熱鬧。呢啲設計唔使諗都做到，但如果政府認為香港回歸20周年呢件事好重要，係咪應該諗多啲？」香港沒設計人才？當然不。可是觀乎政府態度，似係靚唔靚唔重要，最緊要做咗！「如果當政府係client，佢哋知唔知自己想點？似乎一開始，佢哋已經畀錯direction設計師。你想講古仔，都要有古仔講先得；你冇古仔，有好靚插圖都冇用。我覺得浪費了向全世界展示香港設計可以做到啲乜嘅機會。」雖然可能好多市民「㷫回歸」多過「慶回歸」，但如果做得好好睇睇至少冇咁嬲。政府就係唔肯畀人唞下。"},{"pid":"f04aa145b79a7c9e51fe8eb707c61250b0f50ea4","tid":251550,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T04:53:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170519/large/1495190686_5c78.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170519%2Flarge%2F1495190686_5c78.jpg&h=2cb2f342&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本地著名設計師蔡楚堅認為政府可能一開始就錯定方向，才生出各個不統一，沒內涵的設計。<br />\n<br />\nSandy提到外國很多周年紀念活動設計皆出色，包括2015年新加坡獨立50周年國慶logo。「它當然不是非常非常好，但如果跟回歸20周年那個比較，你都會選它吧？」他又大讚今年第41屆香港國際電影節的logo設計。「用咗以前啲人寫嘅數目字花碼，有香港傳統元素，望落有現代感又簡單。」香港設計水平當然不只停留在街坊會，只要政府肯放手，香港設計絕對能登大雅之堂。<br />\n<br />\n我們就HK20圖像用現成素材一事，也訪問了設計博客中央聖學子。他認為設計師總算有將素材拼合構圖，未至於非原創。「呢類小童都能製作嘅畫面，竟要上網download，除咗懶，我諗唔到其他原因。」他形容設計毫不專業，品味庸俗，影響市容（下刪千字），一出街就眼冤！<br />\n<br />\n主權移交後，政府所用嘅政治視覺語言，佢以「虛偽」總結，「試圖以低水平設計粉飾太平，例如起錨、築福香港等。嗰啲創意圖像強調全城喜慶，你講就係呀？」<br />\n<br />\n講起官方設計，佢諗起2002年政府發行紫色膠質新10蚊紙。佢覺得設計奇醜，又異於當時的鈔票設計系統，令設計業界嘩然。當年時任金管局總裁任志剛辯稱：「設計嘅嘢，見仁見智。」佢話：「行之有效嘅鈔票色系，一夜間徹底破壞。你估英國人會唔會有咁獨特嘅品味？」<br />\n<br />\n記者：葉青霞<br />\n攝影：劉永發"},{"pid":"ba787423d7ebca20bcff8fc3b88498838cc6fe86","tid":251550,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T04:54:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170519/large/1495190688_d0cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170519%2Flarge%2F1495190688_d0cb.jpg&h=d61f3f29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n走在街上隨處見到語法羞家的中英文口號，教授認為失敗得很。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170519/large/1495190689_c8e0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170519%2Flarge%2F1495190689_c8e0.jpg&h=557c3eea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蔡楚堅大讚黃新滿設計的第41屆香港國際電影節的宣傳logo設計。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170519/large/1495190690_bd78.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170519%2Flarge%2F1495190690_bd78.jpg&h=a2011e37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國皇家藝術學院175周年慶logo用了很多顏色，配合幾何圖形數字，不覺繁雜。古典徽號與新元素結合沒予人衝突感。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170519/large/1495190691_3a12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170519%2Flarge%2F1495190691_3a12.jpg&h=c2546b50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新加坡獨立50周年國慶簡潔搶眼，放在不同背景都很清楚。"},{"pid":"a596f057374de631c061147c5755b88a63e9e828","tid":251550,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T04:54:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170519/large/1495190618_3bdc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170519%2Flarge%2F1495190618_3bdc.jpg&h=3ce633ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府是是但但已經唔係新聞，慶回歸活動除咗啲設計唔見得人之外，就連口號都令人嘆為觀止。中文版「同心創前路 掌握新機遇」， 講對仗工整，完全唔合格。睇埋英文版Together．Progress．Opportunity，真係想喊。 我請香港大學語言學系教授Stephen Matthews（馬詩帆）評論。懂廣東話嘅佢一見到就話：「冇眼睇。應該冇畀母語係英文嘅人看過，如果唔係佢一定即刻講唔用得。就咁樣三個字根本唔make sense，唔明白意思。」佢認為三個字非同一類別，Together是副詞；Progress可以是名詞或動詞；Opportunity是名詞。「好似word salad，將啲生字撈埋一碟。係Together we can have progress（我們一起邁進）？你要加好多字先有呢個意思，睇慣英文嘅人理解時唔慣要自己補咁多字。我覺得任何主修繙譯嘅學生都可以創作到好啲嘅口號。」<br />\n<br />\n記者：葉青霞<br />\n攝影：劉永發"},{"pid":"1ed41927face6101b17f36897cd57c93220b55fe","tid":251550,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T05:07:56.000Z","msg":"水已笠，理撚得你"},{"pid":"36ccc38373113cfc05cc407ddb1f6a545442a907","tid":251550,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T05:09:40.000Z","msg":"慶回歸口號，好似小童群益會之類標語 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n宣傳片及聲帶，則好似 VTC 宣傳風格 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f0c9f40e69aa070ad620ba413d580d77fb72198","tid":251550,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T09:22:48.000Z","msg":"因為根本不值得慶祝 求奇得啦"},{"pid":"2887ae4223f8b80b27b5ff7ef0d344fd9fbdf51d","tid":251550,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T09:24:24.000Z","msg":"點睇得出新加玻個logo 好？"},{"pid":"246c8aad57c6e3493748471401c2370a6267339a","tid":251550,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T09:26:21.000Z","msg":"素材=唔好？<br />\n咩邏輯？"},{"pid":"4c25700b1703d66dbae31954e061cdf0e78a076d","tid":251550,"uid":11526,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T09:33:09.000Z","msg":"個logo幾寫實<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n回歸二十年一塌糊塗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f66624da0e31729d2de76c2a09e704b5177e974e","tid":251550,"uid":21480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T09:35:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"511834d7afdcea3b72b89e92e1f123d6816e02cc","tid":251550,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T09:35:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>素材=唔好？<br />\n咩邏輯？</blockquote><br />\n素材&ne;唔好<br />\n但真係做得好柒"},{"pid":"029163cda9019da7ab9bf836731528baff0ccf8c","tid":251550,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T09:37:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點睇得出新加玻個logo 好？</blockquote><br />\n第一眼睇以為係sogo<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n新加坡嗰個SG50抄印尼70<br />\n柒到俾人屌"},{"pid":"caa651ed50d3cd22c764e801de45c4e20392beaf","tid":251550,"uid":57723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T09:38:05.000Z","msg":"好親香港<br />\n回歸20年 掘地掘到一撻撻<br />\n五顏六色 三不象 無創意"},{"pid":"5e18d2780ccdb21c6d858c0352eabf8da8b692cb","tid":251550,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T09:42:29.000Z","msg":"又洗左幾多百萬？"},{"pid":"9ca56097ee6b68190e6c2c46918ea1a51b203e0f","tid":251550,"uid":349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T09:48:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點睇得出新加玻個logo 好？</blockquote><br />\n第一眼睇以為係sogo<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n新加坡嗰個SG50抄印尼70<br />\n柒到俾人屌</blockquote><br />\n睇左好耐先發現唔係Sogo 50週年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28d37698768d986a07173a260e7d374bc151cf54","tid":251550,"uid":112197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T09:57:59.000Z","msg":"英國嗰個點樣冇衝突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇一個元素相同 有冇專家解釋吓點為之有衝突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e49c5caf571560c34ca4e248a945dbb50542343f","tid":251550,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T10:03:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好親香港<br />\n回歸20年 掘地掘到一撻撻<br />\n五顏六色 三不象 無創意</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n喻意社會撕裂"},{"pid":"9d9739f10ff14ea807ed344abd8dcbca3069b115","tid":251550,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T10:04:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點睇得出新加玻個logo 好？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為 little red dot<br />\n<br />\n如果唔知乜野係星架坡 little red dot<br />\n<br />\n可以google一下"},{"pid":"54dce058cbd1a814774261c34436bb3c987a961f","tid":251550,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T10:07:27.000Z","msg":"班友曲線啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7fa7d8f25fbe1a8feef33056310787ef0c63793","tid":251550,"uid":72433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T10:43:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/b/b7/%E7%AC%AC40%E5%B1%86%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%E7%AF%80%E4%B8%BB%E9%A1%8C%E8%A8%AD%E8%A8%88.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fb%2Fb7%2F%25E7%25AC%25AC40%25E5%25B1%2586%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E7%25AF%2580%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E9%25A1%258C%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E8%25A8%2588.jpg&h=3e09f648&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我反而覺得第40屆靚D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d7780a2bfc11b9840e909e383c5f0411d97e75c","tid":251550,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T11:19:28.000Z","msg":"識設計就唔係公墓猿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3825226fe543d8596f118d6efedf1c8bcc9ac6e4","tid":251550,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T20:00:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170519/large/1495190689_c8e0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170519%2Flarge%2F1495190689_c8e0.jpg&h=557c3eea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蔡楚堅大讚黃新滿設計的第41屆香港國際電影節的宣傳logo設計。</blockquote><br />\n我真係唔識，但個人覺得呢個唔得，唔睇字都唔知佢做乜，圖又唔知同電影有乜關係"},{"pid":"3c87cbf96c08039fb3753aadd79573f3f8cca21e","tid":251550,"uid":115888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T20:04:32.000Z","msg":"個垃圾設計係PowerPoint水準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cce326391a156fd306cf3a8426221716b53fcc6a","tid":251550,"uid":41954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T20:07:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/b/b7/%E7%AC%AC40%E5%B1%86%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%E7%AF%80%E4%B8%BB%E9%A1%8C%E8%A8%AD%E8%A8%88.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fb%2Fb7%2F%25E7%25AC%25AC40%25E5%25B1%2586%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E7%25AF%2580%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E9%25A1%258C%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E8%25A8%2588.jpg&h=3e09f648&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我反而覺得第40屆靚D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪又係同一個人整"}]}